# Profile overrides for local development (dev).
# Select the profile by exporting APP_ENV in your shell (dev is the default):
#   APP_ENV=dev uv run uvicorn api.main:app --reload
# Copy to .env.dev (gitignored). Loaded after the base .env, so values here win.

